Patch Set 2: Code-Review-1

Can we just find a place to encode all headers?

In the past, we've had several issues with encodings (headers and contents) and that required putting band-aids everywhere. It'd be good to find a single place were we can just go through the headers and encode them.

So far, this has been done by the wsgi server, AFAIK
